Infra seen in reporting (don’t visit) :

clawdbot.getintwopc[.]site (config fetch) 

meeting.bulletmailer[.]net:8041 (phones home)

The extension name: “ClawdBot Agent – AI Coding Assistant”
Extension ID: clawdbot.clawdbot-agent
Published: Jan 27, 2026
Microsoft has since removed it.
New supply-chain bait just hit devs: a fake Moltbot (formerly Clawdbot) “AI coding assistant” made it onto the official VS Code Marketplace… and it drops malware.
